      "span_text": "The lowestenergy conformer of performic acid (labeled (Z,Z) in ref [CITATION_1] features a five-center hydrogen bond and has a calculated adiabatic ionization energy of 10.87 eV. The other stable conformer, (E,E), has no hydrogen bond and has a calculated adiabatic ionization energy that is 0.22 eV lower.",
